<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> <%= locals.title ? title : "Login System" %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-u1OknCvxWvY5kfmNBILK2hRnQC3Pr17a+RTT6rIHI7NnikvbZlHgTPOOmMi466C8" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
</head>
<style>
    .page{
        height: 85vh;
    }
    .content{
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
    }
    .text{
        width: 60%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-around;
        height: 50%;
    }

    .text .heading{
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 10px;
    }

    .text .para{
        width: 80%;
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 10px;
    }
    .images{
        width: 40%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .images .top{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .images .bottom{
        padding: 20px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
    }
    .images img{
        height: 200px;
        width: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .con{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo"><img src="/static/assets/logo.png" alt=""></div>
        <div class="nav">
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="/">Citizen Login</a></div>
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="/route/collectorLogin">Collector Login</a></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="text">
                <div class="heading">
                    <h1>About Us</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="para">
                    <p>The initiative to make <b>Wall-E Waste</b> was taken in a Hackathon event. During the event our team found the need to recycle E-Waste as a necessary step to sustainable development. </p>
                    <p>We are driven with great passions to make something good of this initiative.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="images">
                <div class="top">
                    <div class="con">
                        <img src="/static/assets/Rishabh.jpeg" alt="">
                        <span>Rishabh Kumar</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="con">
                        <img src="/static/assets/Shruti.jpeg" alt="">
                        <span>Shruti Verma</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bottom">
                    <div class="con">
                        <img src="/static/assets/Vinay.jpeg" alt="">
                        <span>Vinay Agarwal</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="con">
                        <img src="/static/assets/Sakshi.jpeg" alt="">
                        <span>Sakshi Kukal</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>